WEBVTT

00:00:02.840 --> 00:00:06.690
Arrow, where are you headed?

00:00:08.690 --> 00:00:11.110
We're going to shoot him, too?

00:00:11.110 --> 00:00:16.370
That young man will be the 
sixth new Stand user...

00:00:16.370 --> 00:00:19.060
But that should be plenty.

00:00:19.060 --> 00:00:24.290
I'll be able to kill anyone who tries 
to get near my son, Yoshikage!

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:30.820
T<c.color6d9396>i</c><c.color709598>n</c><c.color96bcbb>g</c>

00:00:31.030 --> 00:00:32.010
What?!

00:00:37.340 --> 00:00:38.010
Ow.

00:00:38.010 --> 00:00:40.450
Wh-What's the meaning of this?

00:00:40.450 --> 00:00:44.520
The arrow chose him, but it was deflected.

00:01:00.450 --> 00:01:01.700
Jojo's Bizarre Adventure

00:01:00.450 --> 00:01:01.700
Diamond is Unbreakable

